Design a premium mobile app onboarding screen for "SplitEasy" — 
a bill splitting app. This is slide 1 of 3 in a welcome carousel.
Show the screen completely flat and front-facing — no device angle, 
no perspective tilt. Screen fills the entire frame edge to edge.
390x844px canvas.

BACKGROUND:
A smooth vertical gradient. Top: #1E1B4B (near-black dark indigo). 
Bottom: #3730A3 (indigo 700). Same dark, deep, premium feel as the 
splash screen — this is intentional visual continuity. The user is 
still in the welcome emotional space. No electric blue, no neon, 
no banding. Perfectly smooth.

STATUS BAR (top 44px):
Left: "9:41" white Inter 600 15px.
Center: Dynamic Island — black pill 126x37px, 12px from top.
Right: signal, wifi, battery icons in white.

SKIP BUTTON (top right):
"Skip" — Inter 500, 14px, white at 55% opacity.
20px from right edge, 72px from top.
No border, no background — just text, barely there.

ILLUSTRATION AREA (centered horizontally, upper third of screen,
roughly 200px tall, centered around y=280):

Glow backdrop behind the illustration:
A soft circular radial glow, 200px diameter, white at 7% opacity.
Not a visible circle — just a very subtle brightening of the 
background behind the avatars. Barely perceptible.

Three overlapping avatar circles representing three people 
splitting a bill together:

Left avatar: 52px circle, color #818CF8 (soft indigo-purple).
White border 1.5px at 25% opacity around the circle.
Letter "A" centered inside — Inter 700, 18px, white.
Positioned left of center.

Center avatar: 52px circle, color #6366F1 (brand indigo).
White border 1.5px at 25% opacity.
Letter "B" centered inside — Inter 700, 18px, white.
Sits 4px HIGHER than the left and right avatars — 
slightly elevated, suggesting this person paid the bill.
Has an additional very subtle ring behind it: 
64px circle, white at 10% opacity.

Right avatar: 52px circle, color #4F46E5 (deeper indigo).
White border 1.5px at 25% opacity.
Letter "C" centered inside — Inter 700, 18px, white.
