OVERALL FEEL:
This screen sells a feeling, not a feature. 
The three overlapping avatars with amounts below them 
tell the entire story without a single word of explanation.
Dark, premium, considered. Same visual language as the splash screen.
The illustration is geometric and clean — no gradients inside 
the avatars, no textures, no drop shadows on the circles.
Flat, modern, confident.

The screen should feel like it belongs to the same app family 
as the splash screen — same darkness, same indigo palette, 
same typographic precision. A user swiping from splash to 
this screen should feel continuity, not a jarring change.

Render as a flat UI screen, perfectly front-facing,
ultra sharp, no device frame, no mockup angle,
no photography effects, no lens flare. Pure screen design.